incident_updates.body: We have new information regarding the incident that affected your service(s). Please find below an update on the situation: Update : A fix has been implemented and there has been no further impact since 15/07/2025 09:46 UTC Ongoing Actions : We are now monitoring the incident. We will keep you updated on the progress and resolution. We apologize for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.

We are currently experiencing an ongoing incident affecting our Backbone offering, which is causing temporary latency issue in US regions. Here are some supplementary details : Start time : 12/07/2025 17:49 UTC Impacted Service(s) : Latency on our backbone network between CHI and BHS may affect transit through this region. Customers Impact : Customers may experience latency in US Region. Root cause : This incident is caused by a fiber cut. Ongoing Actions : The incident has been identified and our provider are mobilised to restore service as quickly as possible. We will keep you updated on the progress and resolution. We apologize for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.
